            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1647942042360-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1647942042360-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sandwich the<strong> BBQ pulled pork</strong>,<strong> </strong>an<strong> outer lettuce leaf</strong> and some <strong>ranch dressing</strong> between your <strong>toasted brioche halves </strong>with your<strong> smoky fries</strong>, <strong>roasted sweetcorn cobettes</strong> and <strong>lettuce quarters </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> remaining ranch dressing</strong> over the lettuce quarters and top with your <strong>crispy onions</strong>, then spread your <strong>feta & quick-pickled chilli </strong>over the roasted sweetcorn cobettes (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
